des: KNEO Radio operates in the Neosho-Joplin area of Southwest Missouri on the 91.7fm signal and all over the world online at www.kneo.org. It is KNEO's duty to provide you with the programming you need to be an informed Christian. If you like programs such as Focus On The Family, Family Talk, In Touch, Living On The Edge, and much more, you will love KNEO! KNEO is about 85% Christian Talk and Politics and 15% music. The music is a mix of Christian Country and Millennial worship.
